=head1 DESCRIPTION

Information about the property value used in automation of a numeric
questions. Label values are associated with minimum and maximum values
for the numeric question.

=over

=item *

Sentiment scores have a minimum value of -5 and maximum value of 5.

=item *

Duration labels, such as C<NON_TALK_TIME>, C<CONTACT_DURATION>,
C<AGENT_INTERACTION_DURATION>, C<CUSTOMER_HOLD_TIME> have a minimum
value of 0 and maximum value of 63072000.

=item *

Percentages have a minimum value of 0 and maximum value of 100.

=item *

C<NUMBER_OF_INTERRUPTIONS> has a minimum value of 0 and maximum value
of 1000.

=back


=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Label => Str

The property label of the automation.



